Underwriters benefit from live risk monitoring for more accurate pricing.
Operations/claims savings through fewer catastrophic losses.
Portfolio-level insights for risk management and reinsurance optimization.', NULL, NULL, '{}', '{"IoT sensor platforms","PowerUp analytics layer","underwriting PAS (UKRIS/DxC PAS)","Claims Center","client-facing dashboards.","Claims Database"}', '{"Claims Teams",IT/Technology}', 'medium', 3, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, false, false, 'true', 'false', 'false', 'true');
